commit.message:
Add inline type annotations

This commit moves type annotations from the stub file into the main
files, reducing the effort required to use the type hints.

This commit also removes the claim that this library supports python2.
Previous commits had already added code importing the `typing` module,
which was only introduced in python version 3.5.
